Medicare API Endpoint Classes

Source: R/S7_care.R
medicare.Rd

Medicare API Endpoint Classes

Usage

care_endpoint(alias)

care_temporal(alias)

care_group(alias, call = caller_env(), ...)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

call

<env> environment to use for error reporting

...

Additional arguments passed to the group constructor

Value

An S7 <care_endpoint>, or <care_temporal> object

Examples
